{"tid":889124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"殮房遺體被挖雙眼　湖南醫院：家屬有主要監管責任","createTime":"2018-11-04T10:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T09:38:18.000Z","uid":122,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f449a910436d41077e1584d32c51c907eb458e52","tid":889124,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:18:40.000Z","msg":"湖南寧鄉市人民醫院上周二（30日）發生遺體雙眼被挖走事件，警方翌日以涉嫌盜竊、侮辱屍體罪拘捕4名疑犯。事後涉事醫院流出將殮房服務外判傳聞，醫院上周五（2日）發聲明否認，更反指家屬有責任看護屍體。<br />\n<br />\n院方指，殮房為開放管理，暫時還沒有查到醫務人員牽涉此案。院方又強調，家屬對屍體監管有主要責任，醫院只是協助而已。<br />\n<br />\n寧鄉市委宣傳部表示，事件背後可能牽涉販賣器官組織，當地公安現正調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f5315b1324c47eac5a59c97cbfdf8b20d2f3de","tid":889124,"uid":50745,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:30:37.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bb51aa408fd6e0bc7077654ece9768529eb8a6","tid":889124,"uid":37661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"啲錢擺喺銀行，被銀行員工挪用，咁存戶都係一樣有責任喎。"},{"pid":"75ddd97a0341044d5ccc3ca59b2aeec75139926d","tid":889124,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:32:21.000Z","msg":"銀行:存款被盜戶口持有人有監管責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7741cc5e7039c3fb43af34e408eec7aaddd7599","tid":889124,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00bb51aa408fd6e0bc7077654ece9768529eb8a6","tid":889124,"uid":37661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"啲錢擺喺銀行，被銀行員工挪用，咁存戶都係一樣有責任喎。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"你個唸法同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138eda298